snippet.title: Real Racing 2 Trailer
snippet.description: http://firemint.com/R2 - Real Racing 2 is coming on December 16, 2010. Featuring 30 officially licensed cars, 16 car grid and 16 player online races, and available for all generations of iPhone and iPod touch, Real Racing 2 is the most exhilarating handheld racing game!
